description: Crêpes Up combine Japanese and French crêpe-making traditions with sustainable ingredients. We fill our Crêpes with dreamy ingredients in just the right proportions. Our sweet crepes are made with unprocessed fine-milled flour and filled with fresh ingredients. Savory crêpes are made with organic flour, butter and organic eggs. Whether you've got a sweet side or a savory one, we'll craft you a Crêpe to fall in love with!
name: Crepes Up
